{"tid":1047631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[MAGA] 特朗普將取消給印度和土耳其的最惠國待遇","createTime":"2019-03-05T05:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T06:46:57.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9775e84b5d39cc9da8029ad85381ab721c7c0971","tid":1047631,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"特朗普將取消給印度和土耳其的最惠國待遇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001081718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001081718&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=7a55f9cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001081718</a><br />\n<br />\n印度和土耳其將失去在與美國貿易往來中長期享有的最惠國待遇，這是美國總統唐納德&bull;特朗普(Donald Trump)執政期間全球貿易體系遭遇的最新變動。<br />\n<br />\n在特朗普下達一項命令以後，美國貿易官員在聲明中表示，印度和土耳其不再有資格被列為美國普惠制(GSP)下的受惠發展中國家。<br />\n<br />\n這些貿易官員表示，印度未能確保美國享有「公正合理」的市場準入，而土耳其現在「經濟足夠發達」。<br />\n<br />\n美國的聲明還補充稱：「印度樹立了廣泛的貿易壁壘，對美國商貿造成嚴重負面影響。儘管雙方進行了密集接觸，但印度依舊未能採取必要措施來達到普惠制標準。」<br />\n<br />\n美國決定取消土耳其的最惠國待遇，正值土耳其總統雷傑普&bull;塔伊普&bull;埃爾多安(Recep Tayyip Erdogan)與特朗普關係緊張之際。<br />\n<br />\n這些變動至少要等到美國國會以及印度、土耳其政府收到該通知60天後才會生效。"},{"pid":"087b1833512b63eb1c3f64fe5abd9ce3b1984020","tid":1047631,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:44:07.000Z","msg":"咁支那呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞鳩咖哩唔搞支那係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a2be00bbfbd00dd7dc7dc9418a88304f9d47cc","tid":1047631,"uid":51840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"087b1833512b63eb1c3f64fe5abd9ce3b1984020","tid":1047631,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:44:07.000Z","msg":"咁支那呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞鳩咖哩唔搞支那係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"下一個應該係"},{"pid":"b006c124d9ca5730a358f6498b72bf0d59c2432b","tid":1047631,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:45:44.000Z","msg":"幾時先同世貿反枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪打算畀支那做永久發展中國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136bf172e424db6732fb40ad259f39d89b06d812","tid":1047631,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:46:57.000Z","msg":"果然習大大先係侵侵嘅Best Friend <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}